{
  "stem": "232.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We, we stopped on, on big stations.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We had to be fed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There was no food on the train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So on the train stations-- it was war time-- there was Red Cross, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] like, not stores, but stands who served milk and bread to the children and coffee.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And later on, they knew that refugee trains are coming.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And on major stations, people were received.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Like when the train came, it stopped.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We could go out and, and take things-- not buying, because we didn't have money, but to get food and milk and whatever people need.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And a lot of time happened, that-- I know from a-- from a case, a mother was with two children in the train.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And the father went out to get the milk.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And the train left.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And the father was gone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And, and there was no-- you could not run after the train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "It was not a regular train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "There was not a scheduled train who came to, to the next station.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And you can say, I'll go out and wait for the next train for my husband.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It is called-- this village was called Luchon, Bagneres-de-Luchon.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It is-- it is a, a spa, a beautiful spa, a little village.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And where the village ends, you have mountains, the Pyrenees, I mean, rocks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This village alone is about 1,200 feet already-- 1,200 meters above sea level.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Going into this, we went through mountains.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, I never have seen mountains in my life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were always flatlands, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were-- we were infiltrated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In, in France, there were, 'Fifth Column,' they called them, German parachutists.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They parachuted as priests down to, to, to France and mixed in with refugees.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
